========================================================
	Usage: svchost.exe [install | uninstall | app | /?]
	  Options:
	     install - to install the service
	             - after installation, start service with "net start qcmtusvc"
	     uninstall - to uninstall the service
	     app - to run in application/console mode
	     /? - to print this usage info

	  *IMPORTANT*: run from a Cmd Prompt launched "As Admin"
